>200GB/month data transfer</li><li>SolusVM</li><li><b>$3.99/month</b> (OpenVZ \u2014 <a href=\"http://my.bigbrainhost.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=65\">Sign up link</a>), or<br><b>$4.99/month</b> (Xen \u2014 <a href=\"http://my.bigbrainhost.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=55\">Sign up link</a>)</li></ul><p>Also noted that these are more expensive than <a href=\"/blog/bigbrainhost-3-99-128mb-xen2-99-256mb-openvz-vps-exclusive-offer/\">what BigBrainHost has offered a month ago</a>. The previous test IP does not seem to ping anymore. They are still having adjacent DNS (on the same box it seems). Domain registered for 5 months.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fbigbrainhost-3-99-openvz4-99-xen-vps-with-128mb%2F&amp;t=BigBrainHost%20-%20%243.99%20OpenVZ%2F%244.99%20Xen%20VPS%20with%20128MB\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=BigBrainHost%20-%20%243.99%20OpenVZ%2F%244.99%20Xen%20VPS%20with%20128MB&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fbigbrainhost-3-99-openvz4-99-xen-vps-with-128mb%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=